{"type":"message","id":"2f234d7f","parentId":"98f17c7b","timestamp":"2026-05-21T19:21:25.798Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"TanStack Start doesn't use a traditional `index.html` - it generates one during the build process. Let me check if we can build this project. But first, I need to check if `bun` is available since the project uses `bun.lock`.\n\nAlso, I should understand what the user actually wants. Let me re-read the request: \"Integrate it/ replace the control ui with design and theming from the ui\"\n\nI think the most practical approach is:\n1. Try to build the cockpit project\n2. See what output it produces\n3. If it produces static files, we can integrate them\n4. If not, we might need to extract the design system\n\nLet me check if bun is available and try to build.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_lE7yv2qzgTIaebSCuUi32QOR","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which bun && bun --version || echo \"bun not found\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi","model":"kimi-for-coding","usage":{"input":833,"output":183,"cacheRead":52992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54008,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779391277124,"responseId":"msg_AqxqQCN4YZNB4GyaEhP42iGR"}}
