{"type":"message","id":"2727ceba","parentId":"b82d4674","timestamp":"2026-05-21T19:27:15.408Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The prerendering failed because it's looking for `dist/server/server.js` but the build output is `dist/server/index.js`. The @lovable.dev/vite-tanstack-config must have a different server entry naming. Let me check what's in dist/server and see if I can fix the server entry path.\n\nActually, looking at the error, the prerenderer expects `server.js` but we have `index.js`. This is because the vite config uses `server: { entry: \"server\" }` which maps to `src/server.ts`, but the build output is `dist/server/index.js` because of the Cloudflare worker entry configuration.\n\nLet me check the dist/server directory and see if I can create a symlink or copy the file.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_HfnkLvulcKsx2wnwIp29QXZB","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /Users/asherlewis/.openclaw/workspace/openclaw-cockpit/dist/server/","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi","model":"kimi-for-coding","usage":{"input":2605,"output":200,"cacheRead":62976,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65781,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779391627554,"responseId":"msg_uyvhivXEu9mr85TXtW3x5S3a"}}
