{"type":"message","id":"a3a7fe2b","parentId":"eff39b4b","timestamp":"2026-05-21T19:27:31.263Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me try running the build again to see if prerendering works now. But wait, the build will overwrite the dist directory. I should instead change the vite config to output the server entry as `server.js` instead of `index.js`, or add a post-build step.\n\nActually, looking at the error again, it's the preview server plugin looking for `server.js`. The build output is `index.js` because the wrangler config or cloudflare plugin names it that way. Let me check the wrangler.json and see if we can change the output file name.\n\nLet me read the wrangler.json.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_Ab8JNHX99lCNcWBgpsG6oqUC","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/asherlewis/.openclaw/workspace/openclaw-cockpit/wrangler.jsonc"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi","model":"kimi-for-coding","usage":{"input":251,"output":166,"cacheRead":65792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66209,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779391641826,"responseId":"msg_GtIpap8RIs9nLT4LwVRPsS2t"}}
