{"type":"message","id":"015751c1","parentId":"f1aa84fb","timestamp":"2026-05-21T19:29:40.871Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The prerendered HTML looks great! It's a fully static HTML file with all the content pre-rendered. Now I can:\n\n1. Copy these static files to replace the OpenClaw control UI\n2. Update asset paths to be relative (since the control UI might be served from a subdirectory)\n3. Update workspace docs\n\nLet me now:\n1. Copy the dist/client files to the OpenClaw control-ui directory\n2. Fix any absolute paths to relative paths\n3. Update TOOLS.md and other docs\n\nFirst, let me backup the existing control UI and then replace it with the cockpit build.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_68y6OOUaIuIW0PhieuqmTxjT","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/bin/zsh\n# Build and deploy cockpit as OpenClaw control UI\n\nset -e\n\nCOCKPIT_DIR=\"/Users/asherlewis/.openclaw/workspace/openclaw-cockpit\"\nCONTROL_UI_DIR=\"/Users/asherlewis/.openclaw/extensions/kimi-claw/node_modules/openclaw/dist/control-ui\"\nBACKUP_DIR=\"/Users/asherlewis/.openclaw/extensions/kimi-claw/node_modules/openclaw/dist/control-ui-backup\"\n\n# Export bun path\nexport PATH=\"$HOME/.bun/bin:$PATH\"\n\necho \"🔧 Building cockpit...\"\ncd \"$COCKPIT_DIR\"\nbun run build || true  # Build may exit with error after prerender, but files are generated\n\necho \"📦 Backing up existing control UI...\"\nif [ -d \"$CONTROL_UI_DIR\" ]; then\n    rm -rf \"$BACKUP_DIR\" 2>/dev/null || true\n    cp -R \"$CONTROL_UI_DIR\" \"$BACKUP_DIR\"\nfi\n\necho \"🚀 Replacing control UI with cockpit...\"\nrm -rf \"$CONTROL_UI_DIR\"/*\ncp -R \"$COCKPIT_DIR/dist/client/\"* \"$CONTROL_UI_DIR/\"\n\necho \"🔧 Fixing asset paths...\"\n# Convert absolute paths to relative paths in all HTML files\nfind \"$CONTROL_UI_DIR\" -name \"*.html\" -exec sed -i '' 's|href=\"/assets/|href=\"./assets/|g' {} \\;\nfind \"$CONTROL_UI_DIR\" -name \"*.html\" -exec sed -i '' 's|src=\"/assets/|src=\"./assets/|g' {} \\;\nfind \"$CONTROL_UI_DIR\" -name \"*.html\" -exec sed -i '' 's|import(\"/assets/|import(\"./assets/|g' {} \\;\n\necho \"✅ Done! Control UI replaced with cockpit.\"\necho \"📍 Location: $CONTROL_UI_DIR\"\necho \"🔄 Restart OpenClaw gateway to see changes.\"\n","path":"/Users/asherlewis/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/deploy-cockpit.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi","model":"kimi-for-coding","usage":{"input":3330,"output":623,"cacheRead":74496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78449,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779391763065,"responseId":"msg_D1In0uDeCd1wpwr2PFhgRK3D"}}
