{"type":"message","id":"c9b5c054","parentId":"f9e856b1","timestamp":"2026-05-21T19:30:11.746Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The control UI has been replaced. But I notice the favicon files are missing from the new control-ui directory. Let me check if there are any issues with the replacement and also copy the favicon files from the backup or from the cockpit.\n\nActually, looking at the cockpit's `__root.tsx`, it doesn't include favicon links. The original control UI had favicons. Let me check if we need to add them or if the backup preserved them.\n\nAlso, I should check the `index.html` in the new control-ui to make sure paths are correct.\n\nLet me also update TOOLS.md to document the cockpit and the deployment script.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_3VGj07JS0J51M3kNJw5x3q6M","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"## 🌐 Services & Endpoints (Local)\n\n| Service | Port | Stack | Status |\n|---------|------|-------|--------|\n| RoleVault Postgres | `5433` | Standalone | ✅ Running |\n| BionicGPT | `7703` | docker-compose | ⏹️ Stopped |\n| Forgejo | `3000` | docker-compose | ⏹️ Stopped |\n| LobeHub | `3210` | docker-compose | ⏹️ Stopped |\n| MinIO | `9000-9001` | docker-compose | ⏹️ Stopped |\n| **OpenClaw Cockpit** | `18789` | Built static | ✅ Replaces Control UI |\n\n### OpenClaw Cockpit (Control UI Replacement)\n- **Location**: `~/.openclaw/workspace/openclaw-cockpit/`\n- **Build**: `bun run build` (produces `dist/client/` static files)\n- **Deploy**: `~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/deploy-cockpit.sh`\n- **Design**: Dark-first, oklch-based, Tailwind v4, shadcn/ui components\n- **Tech**: TanStack Start + React 19 + Vite + Cloudflare Workers (SSR → static prerender)\n- **Pages**: Chat (`/`), Images (`/images`), Videos (`/videos`), Library (`/library`), Settings (`/settings`)\n- **Features**: Endpoint management, chat with caching, streaming, thread history, provider status","oldText":"## 🌐 Services & Endpoints (Local)\n\n| Service | Port | Stack | Status |\n|---------|------|-------|--------|\n| RoleVault Postgres | `5433` | Standalone | ✅ Running |\n| BionicGPT | `7703` | docker-compose | ⏹️ Stopped |\n| Forgejo | `3000` | docker-compose | ⏹️ Stopped |\n| LobeHub | `3210` | docker-compose | ⏹️ Stopped |\n| MinIO | `9000-9001` | docker-compose | ⏹️ Stopped |"}],"path":"/Users/asherlewis/.openclaw/workspace/TOOLS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi","model":"kimi-for-coding","usage":{"input":444,"output":636,"cacheRead":79872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80952,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779391796799,"responseId":"msg_ydZ6LUcD3MTLfIymQBCcXKI9"}}
