{"type":"message","id":"81d87188","parentId":"63843b16","timestamp":"2026-05-21T19:31:01.640Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me provide a summary of what was accomplished.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Done. The cockpit is now integrated and has replaced the OpenClaw Control UI.\n\n**What happened:**\n- Built the `openclaw-cockpit` project (TanStack Start + React 19 + Tailwind v4)\n- Configured static prerendering so it generates static HTML files\n- Created `scripts/deploy-cockpit.sh` that builds and copies the output to `node_modules/openclaw/dist/control-ui/`\n- Ran the deploy — your Control UI at `http://localhost:18789/` now serves the cockpit\n\n**The cockpit features:**\n- Dark-first design with animated hue-cycling background\n- Chat interface with streaming, caching, and endpoint management\n- Pages: Chat (`/`), Images, Videos, Library, Settings\n- shadcn/ui components with oklch-based color system\n- Provider status indicators, thread history, endpoint configuration\n\n**To redeploy after editing:**\n```bash\n~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/deploy-cockpit.sh\n```\n\n**To develop:**\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/openclaw-cockpit\nbun run dev        # dev server on :8080\nbun run build      # static build (with prerender)\n```\n\n**Note:** The prerender build throws a harmless `process.stdin.off` error at the very end (Node.js compat issue with Vite), but all 5 pages get generated successfully before that. The deploy script handles it.\n\nAll changes are committed to the workspace git repo."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi","model":"kimi-for-coding","usage":{"input":261,"output":318,"cacheRead":86016,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86595,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779391849910,"responseId":"msg_sklUjEDHrTuBzGuTq60m7Gn5"}}
